op_master_id:
(SELECT
  RTRIM(TR.TRCD) AS TRCD
  ,TR.ZIP
  ,TR.ADDR1
  ,TR.ADDR2
  ,TR.TEL
  ,TR.FAX
  ,FR.MEIGI
  ,FR.MEIGIK
  ,SK.SKBKIND
  ,FR.YOKIN_TYP
  ,FR.KOUZA
  ,FR.TESUU
  ,FR.SOUKIN
  ,FR.BANK_CD
  ,FR.SITEN_ID
  ,SH.SIHARAIDD
  ,SH.SKIJITUDD
  ,SH.V_YAKUJO
  ,TR.KNLD
  ,TR.SBUSYO
  ,TR.STANTO
  ,TR.KEICD
  ,TR.NAYOSE
  ,TR.F_SETUIN
  ,TR.STAN
  ,RTRIM(TR.SBCOD) AS SBCOD
  ,TR.SKICD
  ,TR.F_SOUFU
  ,TR.ANNAI
  ,TR.TSOKBN
  ,TR.F_SHITU
  ,TR.CDM2
  ,TR.DM1
  ,TR.DM2
  ,TR.DM3
  ,FR.GENDO
FROM
  (SELECT TRCD, MIN(HJCD) AS HJCD FROM SS_TORI GROUP BY TRCD) AS TMP_TR
JOIN SS_TORI TR ON
  TR.TRCD = TMP_TR.TRCD AND
  TR.HJCD = TMP_TR.HJCD AND
  TR.SAIMU = 1 
JOIN SS_TSHOH TS ON
  TS.TRCD = TR.TRCD
  AND TS.HJCD = TR.HJCD
  AND TS.SHO_ID = 1
JOIN SS_SHOHO SH ON
  SH.SHINO = TS.SHINO
JOIN SS_SKUBN SK ON
  SK.SKBNCOD = SH.SKBNCOD
JOIN SS_FRIGIN FR ON
  FR.TRCD = TR.TRCD
  AND FR.HJCD = TR.HJCD
  AND FR.GIN_ID = 1
WHERE
  LENGTH(TR.TRCD) < 13)
op_master_name: 取引先マスター（依頼先）
